Name: EFT
About the game: EFT GET READY TO ESCAPE WITH EFT Our adventure starts out with our hero allowing himself to be captured in order to get into a castle dungeon, after he hears a rumor about there being a large and unusual treasure hidden there. But uh-oh! His friend is captured as well. Now, he must find the treasure and find his friend before it is too late. Let's fight you to escape from this dungeon! But watch out for the guards, they can catch you at any time. Be very carefull !
